title: Murder with Rapper Reese Laflare
description:
SLATT! This week the boys are doing a driveby with Grammy-nominated rapper, designer and Atlanta royalty, Reese Laflare. Reese is calling in as he whips around Black Hollywood to talk about discovering TF, personal style, who has trash drip, skaters being the true source, vacation fits, his top 5 dead or alive, retiring, being slept on, what’s going on with his brand Diva, meme stonks, being in the studio with Young Thug and much more on this braggadocios and influential episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
